            <hr>
            <p>Thank you for visiting our website, where you can find medical clinics and doctors and schedule appointments with them. Your privacy is important to us, and we want to ensure that your personal information is protected. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share your personal information when you use our website.</p>
<hr>
