            </ul>
            <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes. However, we may share your personal information with medical clinics and doctors to schedule appointments and provide you with the requested services. We may also share your personal information with our service providers who assist us with website hosting, data analysis, and other services.</p>
            <hr>

            <h3>Your Choices and Rights</h3>
            <p>You have certain choices and rights regarding your personal information:</p>
